form:listbox.form:list-source: SELECT distinct concat(t1.Name,', ',t1.Vorname) as Name,t1.AnsprechpartnerID FROM Ansprechpartner_Kunden as t1 INNER JOIN Angebote1 as t3 ON t1.KontaktID=t3.KontaktID INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID=1 AND t3.DocumentID=t2.DocumentID ORDER BY t1.Name ASC
SELECT distinct concat(t1.Name1,', ',t1.Vorname,' ',t1.Name2,' --> ',t1.Ort) as Name,t1.KontaktID FROM Kunden as t1 ORDER BY t1.Name1 ASC
SELECT distinct Projekt_Name,ProjektID FROM Projekte ORDER BY Projekt_Name ASC

form:listbox.form:list-source: SELECT distinct YEAR(Erstellungsdatum),YEAR(Erstellungsdatum) as Jahr FROM Angebote1 ORDER BY Jahr DESC

SELECT distinct concat(t1.Name1,' ',t1.Vorname,' ',t1.Name2,' --> ',t1.Ort) as Name,t2.KontaktID FROM (Kunden as t1 INNER JOIN Angebote1 as t2 ON t1.KontaktID=t2.KontaktID) INNER JOIN Steuerung as t3 ON t3.ClientID=1 WHERE ((((YEAR(t2.Erstellungsdatum)=t3.Jahr AND LENGTH(t3.Jahr) > 0) OR t2.KontaktID like '%' AND (LENGTH(t3.Jahr) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t3.Jahr)=0))) OR t1.KontaktID=t3.KontaktID) ORDER BY t1.Name1

SELECT DISTINCT t1.Document_Name,t1.DocumentID FROM Steuerung AS t2,Angebote1 as t1 LEFT JOIN Angebote2 AS t3 ON t3.DocumentID=t1.DocumentID AND t3.Leistungsbezeichnung LIKE CONCAT('%',(SELECT Suchstring_2 FROM Steuerung WHERE ClientID=1),'%') WHERE t2.ClientID=1 AND (((YEAR(t1.Erstellungsdatum)=t2.Jahr AND LENGTH(t2.Jahr) > 0) OR (t1.DocumentID like '%' AND (LENGTH(t2.Jahr) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Jahr)=0))) AND ((t1.KontaktID=t2.KontaktID AND LENGTH(t2.KontaktID) > 0) OR (t1.DocumentID like '%' AND (LENGTH(t2.KontaktID) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.KontaktID)=0))) AND ((t1.ProjektID=t2.ProjektID AND LENGTH(t2.ProjektID) > 0) OR (t1.DocumentID like '%' AND (LENGTH(t2.ProjektID) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.ProjektID)=0))) AND (((t1.Document_Name LIKE CONCAT('%',t2.Suchstring_2,'%') AND LENGTH(t2.Suchstring_2) > 0) OR (t1.Document_Name like '%' AND (LENGTH(t2.Suchstring_2) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Suchstring_2)=0))) OR t1.DocumentID=t3.DocumentID) OR t1.DocumentID=t2.DocumentID) ORDER BY t1.DocumentID DESC

SELECT distinct t1.Projekt_Name,t1.ProjektID FROM Projekte as t1 INNER JOIN Angebote1 as t2 ON t1.ProjektID=t2.ProjektID INNER JOIN Steuerung as t3 ON t3.ClientID=1 WHERE ((((YEAR(t2.Erstellungsdatum)=t3.Jahr AND LENGTH(t3.Jahr) > 0) OR t1.ProjektID like '%' AND (LENGTH(t3.Jahr) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t3.Jahr)=0))) AND ((t2.KontaktID=t3.KontaktID AND LENGTH(t3.KontaktID) > 0) OR (t1.ProjektID like '%' AND (LENGTH(t3.KontaktID) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t3.KontaktID)=0))) OR t1.ProjektID=t3.ProjektID) ORDER BY t1.Projekt_Name ASC

form:listbox.form:list-source: SELECT distinct t1.Leistungsbezeichnung,t1.LeistungsID FROM Leistungsstamm as t1 INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID=1 WHERE (((((t1.Leistungsgruppe=t2.GruppenID AND LENGTH(t2.GruppenID) > 0) OR (t1.LeistungsID like '%' AND LENGTH(t2.GruppenID) IS NULL)) AND (((t2.Option_1=1 AND (t1.LeistungsID like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') OR t1.Bestellnummer like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%'))) OR (t2.Option_2=1 AND t1.Leistungsbezeichnung like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%')) OR (t2.Option_3=1 AND t1.Leistungsbeschreibung like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%')) AND LENGTH(t2.Suchstring) > 0) OR (((t2.Option_1=0 AND t2.Option_2=0 AND t2.Option_3=0) OR LENGTH(t2.Suchstring) IS NULL) AND t1.LeistungsID like '%'))) OR t1.Standard=1 OR t1.LeistungsID=t2.LeistungsID)) ORDER BY LeistungsID ASC
